node.text:
My “middle kids” ❤️
I know in a family of three kiddos, there is the oldest, middle and youngest.
And maybe in bigger families the oldest is just meant to be the oldest child and the youngest is the single youngest.
But generally I consider my two eldest to be “the oldest” as they are only 11 months apart and are similar in maturity. I also have two youngest as they’re twins. 🤷🏼‍♀️ So these four are kind of like our middle kids. The triplets were all “the youngest” until the twins were born but now they’ve joined Felix in the middle 😆

If you have more than 3 kids, how many do you consider oldest/middle/youngest? 🤔🥰

node.text:
Happy SIXTH birthday to our sweet little trio ❤️❤️❤️
Henry Magnus, Rufus Murphy & Pearl Miriam.. I can’t believe it’s been six years since we met you for the first time. 🥲
You are each so beautifully individual and yet such a tight unit, little besties 🥰
We love you and we are so so proud of you. ❤️❤️❤️ #triplets #sixtoday

node.text:
Sorry I’ve been a bit MIA. 
This week has been a week.
We had one child fall out of a tree at school, spent the day in hospital getting xrays etc to find out he fractured his elbow 🥺 so is now wearing a sling and learning to do life one-handed.
And then the next day we had a kid fall onto his face at school, leaving a big cut that needed to be glued 🤕
My poor babies 😔❤️

This all came after a week of us all being pretty sick 🤧 so it’s been a little rough thats for sure. 

I’m behind on work requirements too and my house is a mess 🥴 the laundry never ends.. we are getting our first ever clothes dryer delivered to us this weekend because we usually line dry everything but this winter is proving difficult to keep up! Nothing is drying fast enough 🥶

I’m looking forward to the school holidays starting this weekend (for us) so we can take some time to just relax and recharge 🥰 

This will be our first school holidays since starting school. What are some things you like to do during school holidays with kids? 🙏😇

We are loving our new Cushy Sofa Bed from @koala. It’s so comfy and so perfect for sitting, sleeping and snuggling! 🥰
Not only that, but it can be delivered within four hours and assembled tool-free! 🐨
The kids are now planning sleepovers in the living room 😆

#KoalaFurniture #LoungeWithKoala #collab
